data.description: This is it!  The one you have been waiting for! A True 5 Bedroom/3 Bath home! The moment you walk in the front door you will be amazed at the space! Upon entering you step into a front office/room with a view straight back to an incredible family room with an entire stone wall/fireplace (Smart TV Mounted Conveys and swivels above and below the mantle)  and natural lighting (2 skylights). With 3 bedrooms and 2 baths on the main level,  (one primary with on-suite bath with shower, and walk in closet.  The family room steps down into a 4 season sun room with sliding glass doors.  The kitchen is bright and spacious with lots of cabinets and a laundry room/pantry that leads you to a garage! Wait until you see how big the dining room is!  Invite all the family for those holiday events.   Each bathroom has a fan timer installed! Head upstairs to find an additional full bathroom and 2 more bedrooms with tons of closet space.  But wait - it doesn't stop there!  There is a completely separate building/he-she shed - yes! It has been used as an apartment for family but it can be an office space, with a kitchenette, bathroom with shower!  It has its own electric breaker but is attached to the house electricity).  The rear yard is fenced in so bring your pet along!  This home will soon be snatched up so don't wait!  Brand new roof, water heater, and gas stove/oven, reverse osmosis tank/system at kitchen sink and new farmhouse sink with cutting board, and interchangeable sink bowls.   Seller will entertain all reasonable offers.
